name: Darwin Marketing
overview:
Since 2005, Darwin Marketing has developed as a privately funded China focused internet marketing agency based in Shanghai, China with offices in Beijing since 2008.

Our primary focus for clients is using digital channels such as Search, Social and Display to deliver high ROI value for our clients marketing investments. To date, we have delivered positive ROI on more than 150+ paid search (PPC) campaigns, more than 50+ natural search (SEO) campaigns and many more display campaigns.

Our team includes more than 70+ professionals including internet marketing strategists, channel specific analysts (Search, Social, Display), technologists in charge of creating tools (i.e. SearchValue for integrating paid search), and product managers that develop new services (landing page optimization; usability; internet strategy) that scale our business analysts ability to deliver high ROI for clients.
